Subject: drm/i915/selftests: Check that registers are preserved between
 virtual engines
Git-commit: 86027e312c36dfe6b614e32f7550d5fe20a6d9e0
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
References: bsc#1152489

Make sure that we copy across the registers from one engine to the next,
as we hop around a virtual engine.

Signed-off-by: Chris Wilson <chris@chris-wilson.co.uk>
Cc: Tvrtko Ursulin <tvrtko.ursulin@intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Tvrtko Ursulin <tvrtko.ursulin@intel.com>
